Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西怪怪的  我不知為啥有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視中正在播放的  是跟我一點關係都沒有的同縣選手的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為啥我正支持著正處於落後的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又不知為啥覺得差不多春日要搞點事出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  電話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很閒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩點整全員在車站前集合  老老實實地過來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連一句話都沒說上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘跟你說帶東西來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一套泳裝  還有足夠的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一定要騎自行車來  Over～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了我連一句話都沒說上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像又知道春日打算要說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確地說  是感覺之前好像出現過完全相同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂的「既視感」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就這樣繳槍了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  阿虛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多拿點幹勁出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也才剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  全都到齊了  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去市民游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這準備的架勢來看也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天當然要有夏天的樣子  要做有夏天特色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的時間可是一去不返的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在就要行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個只有一次的高一的暑假裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便我們是騎自行車去泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也騎來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  自行車只有你和我的兩輛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  阿虛  可不能輸給古泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  立即出發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你們兩個趕緊停好車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說阿虛  接下來是要玩啊  你怎麼就筋疲力盡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的錯啊  誰的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這消毒液的氣味  真給人一種實在的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  來游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽哦比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼宮同學  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺歡樂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很歡樂的情景  還真讓人感到和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得  涼宮同學也學會了有常識性的娛樂方法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打個電話過來  單方面地說有事就掛的邀請方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在不能說得上是常識性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那點事  要我說根本不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得那麼開心的涼宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會做什麼震動這個世界的事情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是我的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為從初春開始就發生了太多事情 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得有點神經質了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又輸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希  我們再比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  與其說是市民泳池  倒是個更適合平民泳池這名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼春日會選這樣一個地方來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  與其說是市民泳池  倒是個更適合平民泳池這名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼春日會選這樣一個地方來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  然後春日說了這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個就是我的團員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼他們都會聽的  所以隨便吩咐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  要玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩水中足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  這種事也常有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既視感什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩餘不多的暑假該如何度過的預定表啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然發現  暑假只剩下兩個星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後要趕快地去玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在不到兩週內搞完這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠有什麼想要做的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我想撈金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撈…金…魚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  明天開始實行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近什麼地方有盂蘭盆會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煙火匯演也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了撈金魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是我給錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  今天就此解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  其實也沒有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近如何  精神好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打攪你了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  為什麼我會去和長門搭腔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天早晨  將我的懶覺奪走的又是春日的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是說找到盂蘭盆會的會場了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  地點似乎是市民運動場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  今天你又是最後一個  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了  我們大伙一起去買浴衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日進了女裝的大賣場之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自為朝比奈學姐和長門挑選了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後毫不客氣地衝進了試衣間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我們等了大約一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人終於出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都非常合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦  是我給挑選的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛  太可愛了  真不愧是我挑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐  轉過來！轉過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這麼熱鬧真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盂蘭盆會啊  真虧得能聚集起這麼多人…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了  怎麼又是這種感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有你想要玩的撈金魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去撈個痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去玩吧  來一決高下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個來  長門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  長門  你對那種東西有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  800日元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為啥有種受她照顧的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那種程度的我來買就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三條
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不需要那麼多  就只要了一條
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃一個的話沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那面具哪裡弄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下來玩煙火吧  煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是夏天  在暑假中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  雖然極力想要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有件事情卻讓我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  明天是捉昆蟲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日啊  雖說玩也沒問題  你暑假作業做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼嘛  那種程度的作業有三天不就全部做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three days！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種麻煩事就得事先趕緊收拾掉再玩到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是正確的享受暑假的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種傢伙腦子這麼好  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天對於人的參數調整還真是隨便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  明天去捉昆蟲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉到的蟲子最多的那個人  怎麼好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就把團長的權力讓給他一天！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣呢  只要是蟲子的話什麼都可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…只能抓蟬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這就是SOS團內部的捉蟬大戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  是個讓人有種「連這也是啊」的感覺的大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS團內部的捉蟬大戰就在這大晴天下進行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說大家都在努力奮鬥  可應該說不出所料還是說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲勝者是春日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底  還是要有放生的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放它們一條生路  以後說不定會來報恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟬來了到底能為我們做些啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回山裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點打開了盒子的潘多拉的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡…歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  我們在一無所知的情況下被套上了青蛙的罩衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始在超市的門口兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這待遇差算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長大叔也謝謝大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要大叔的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:12:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很早之前就很想要這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也看在實玖瑠的份上說送給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就為了這種東西累死累活地幹活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把這放在社團室做紀念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  你想什麼時候穿都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我許可的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上  奪去了我的安眠的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  有非常不好的事情…這樣下去我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:13:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會這個時候跟朝比奈學姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有點情況  你能現在就過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋  你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了  朝比奈學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回不了未來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  事情是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在永久地重複著同樣的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你滿面春光地把那種非現實的話說出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉  你知道自己在說什麼嗎  嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道  相當清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才和朝比奈學姐談了下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是叫上我啊  然後你好回去了  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:15:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後意識到最近這裡時間的流動出現了異常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該說是朝比奈學姐的功績吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託她的福我也確信了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確信什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經重複體驗同樣的時間許多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個剛才就聽你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確地說應該是八月十七日到三十一日之間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正處於一個沒有盡頭的暑假的正當中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在確實是暑假…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對無法結束的Endless Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個世界裡  九月一日之後的時間全部消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要誰相信那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望至少你能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被困在那個叫什麼封鎖空間裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一部分的時間被分割開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:16:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到八月三十一日二十四時整的那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都被重置  再回到十七日的過程
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  全人類的記憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些也會重置  會重頭再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是關於時間這個那個了的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…既然未來人也混進來了  那我覺得也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這件事和朝比奈學姐沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原因是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是涼宮同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然本人沒有這個自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心裡什麼地方總在想著暑假不要結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啥啊  難道留著什麼遺憾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許她是想著暑假還有什麼事情剩下沒做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個\N會把一些莫名其妙的事情展開到大宇宙規模的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了這個的話  就能迎刃而解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我就覺得  你好像樂在其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知你是不是也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近頻繁發生的既視感之迷終於解開了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想來  那只能理解為是由於記憶重置而散落下來的殘渣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  難道說全世界的人都感覺得到這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是這樣  我和你算是特例了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那春日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙多少有一點意識到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說有了反而糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  別說是既視感了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得應該有一個人保存著所有輪迴中的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊  那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說也該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:17:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶問下  這重複現在到底是第幾次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是第15527次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15527？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15527是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門  你在說啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那話是認真的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多的次數  我們全都在重複同樣的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非全部如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15527次中沒有去盂蘭盆會的模式  有第2391次和第11054次的這兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  去了盂蘭盆會而沒有撈金魚的模式有437次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打工的有9052次  其內容有6個模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了發放氣球  還有搬貨物  做收銀員  發送傳單…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第15527次…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門她這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上兩週的話就是…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是595年的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼長的時間僅她一個人能夠好好地保留著記憶  無數次無數次地重複嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門  你到底到現在為止都是以什麼樣的心情度過的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天是觀測天體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點是長門的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天體望遠鏡由古泉準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不希望它存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類第一次踏上火星的時候  一定會從暗處跑出來歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「歡迎來到火星」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找UFO吧  UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底想做啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道的話  也能順利解決了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試下這樣怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從後面突然抱住涼宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她耳邊輕語「I love you」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這由誰來做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你沒有適合的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I…I love you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不要  我要擺脫這種支配
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我來做怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的了  我做這角色還不夠格  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只會讓涼宮同學增加無謂的混亂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之後去了打擊中心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  長門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在朝比奈學姐說出來之前就注意到了這輪迴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼沉默不語
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的工作是觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒濤般的暑假活動消化體制還在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火大會  釣蝦虎魚大會  試膽  電影連看後是海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在活動來活動去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我覺得春日應該不會這樣就滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即便如此  也沒有什麼行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣終於來到了  八月三十日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這樣課題就如實地完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:22:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…也就這樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  還有什麼想做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個暑假已經做了好多事了  已經很充實了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該還沒有滿足才對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天當預備日先空下來了  大家就這樣休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天在社團教室再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊  春…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天當預備日先空下來了  大家就這樣休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.03,0:22:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還前所未有地強烈！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能讓春日回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那重複了一萬幾千次的兩星期又要陷入永遠循環的窘境了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我該做什麼呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在春日的話裡應該有提示的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她至今都說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.14,0:23:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白  我想不起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月三十一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.07,0:23:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業  還沒動過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢  怎麼都成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再重複的話  作業做了也沒意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管明天來不來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  也只能交給那時的我來處理了吧


